    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pachinko Party</strong> is a reimagining of the classic pinball pachinko experience but with a chaotic competitive twist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab you friends, chose a character and get ready to blast your way to victory in multiple game modes or play online against your favourite streamer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093410/extras/7ee99c31deee6dba9c0e0a363bf31e41.avif?t=1754728706\" width=600 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play local and online multiplayer with 4+ players</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A party game classic, sit back and grab up to 4 friends to tackle a tournament of different Pachinko style puzzles and challenges either in local or online multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093410/extras/27aa5b7c641873fe6a7ba1c63f296b30.avif?t=1754728706\" width=600 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Original Game Modes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a full tournament of different game modes including 'Score Attack, 'Hot Peg' and more! Each game is short, fast and an original spin on the classic pachinko gameplay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093410/extras/ffc62c6a3ecb68b504239bfd087252da.avif?t=1754728706\" width=600 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customisable Characters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own partygoer, a representation of you and your character in game! Change everything from eyebrows, shape and colour and lots more.<strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093410/extras/310d668186b93e50dbc677565eaa97fb.avif?t=1754728706\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093410/extras_big/310d668186b93e50dbc677565eaa97fb.avif?t=1754728706 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Streamer support</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will allow for audience participation allows streamers to play against one another using their audiences! (Coming soon)</p>",
